<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>锅炉受热面全寿命管理系统 | v7.3 湛江电厂稳定版</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  :root {
    --bg-0: #00060f; --bg-1: #001122; --bg-2: #001d3d;
    --accent: #00d4ff; --accent-2: #0077b6; --accent-3: #48cae4;
    --glow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.6);
    --text: #e0f7ff; --text-dim: #7fb3d5;
    --danger: #ff3860; --warn: #ffcc00; --ok: #00e676;
  }
  body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; background: var(--bg-0); color: var(--text); overflow-x: hidden; min-height: 100vh; }
  .bg-grid { position: fixed; inset: 0; background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px; z-index: -2; animation: gridMove 20s linear infinite; }
  @keyframes gridMove { 100% { background-position: 40px 40px; } }
  .bg-glow { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: -1; pointer-events: none; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 600px 400px at 10% 20%, rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.15), transparent), radial-gradient(ellipse 500px 500px at 90% 80%, rgba(72, 202, 228, 0.1), transparent); }

  header { padding: 20px 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); background: rgba(0, 6, 15, 0.6); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
  .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; }
  .logo-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; border: 2px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: var(--glow); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .logo-icon::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 40%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3), transparent 60%); animation: shine 3s linear infinite; }
  @keyframes shine { 0%{transform:translateX(-100%);} 100%{transform:translateX(100%);} }
  .logo-icon svg { width: 28px; height: 28px; fill: var(--accent); z-index: 1; }
  .logo-text h1 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fff, var(--accent)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
  .logo-text p { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: 3px; }
  .header-info { display: flex; gap: 25px; align-items: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); }
  .header-info .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--ok); box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--ok); display: inline-block; margin-right: 6px; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;} 50%{opacity:0.4;} }

  nav { display: flex; gap: 4px; padding: 15px 40px; background: rgba(0, 17, 34, 0.4); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1); overflow-x: auto; }
  .nav-btn { padding: 10px 22px; background: transparent; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); color: var(--text-dim); cursor: pointer; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: all 0.3s; white-space: nowrap; font-family: inherit; }
  .nav-btn:hover { color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05); }
  .nav-btn.active { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2), rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.2)); color: #fff; border-color: var(--accent); box-shadow: var(--glow); }
  .nav-btn.ai-btn { border-color: #a29bfe; color: #a29bfe; }
  .nav-btn.ai-btn.active { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(162, 155, 254, 0.3), rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.2)); border-color: #a29bfe; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(162, 155, 254, 0.5); color: #fff; }

  main { padding: 30px 40px 60px; max-width: 1600px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .view { display: none; animation: fadeIn 0.5s; }
  .view.active { display: block; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  .section-title { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15); }
  .section-title::before { content: ''; width: 4px; height: 24px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent), transparent); box-shadow: var(--glow); }
  .section-title h2 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .section-title .sub { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 12px; margin-left: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; }

  .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 18px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .stat-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 29, 61, 0.6), rgba(0, 17, 34, 0.6)); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: all 0.3s; }
  .stat-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: var(--accent); box-shadow: var(--glow); }
  .stat-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent), transparent); }
  .stat-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .stat-value { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5); }
  
  .card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 29, 61, 0.5), rgba(0, 17, 34, 0.5)); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; backdrop-filter: blur(5px); }
  .card-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; color: var(--accent-3); }
  .card-title::before { content: '◆'; color: var(--accent); font-size: 10px; }

  .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .grid-2, .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 15px; }
  .form-group { margin-bottom: 15px; }
  .form-group label { display: block; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 6px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .form-group select, .form-group input, .form-group textarea { width: 100%; padding: 10px 12px; background: rgba(0, 6, 15, 0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3); border-radius: 6px; color: var(--text); font-family: 'Consolas', 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; transition: all 0.3s; }
  .form-group textarea { font-family: inherit; resize: vertical; }
  .form-group select:focus, .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--accent); box-shadow: var(--glow); }
  .form-group select option { background: var(--bg-1); }

  .code-output { margin-top: 20px; padding: 20px; background: rgba(0, 6, 15, 0.8); border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1), var(--glow); }
  .code-output .label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .code-output .code { font-family: 'Consolas', 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 3px; margin-top: 10px; text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.8); word-break: break-all; }
  .code-segment { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 6px; margin: 0 2px; background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 20px; }

  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15); }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
  th { background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.4), rgba(0, 29, 61, 0.6)); padding: 12px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3); color: var(--accent-3); font-size: 12px; white-space: nowrap; }
  td { padding: 11px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08); font-family: 'Consolas', monospace; }
  tr:hover td { background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05); }
  .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .badge-ww { background: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.15); color: var(--ok); border: 1px solid var(--ok); }
  .badge-sh { background: rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.15); color: var(--warn); border: 1px solid var(--warn); }
  .badge-rh { background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15); color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid var(--accent); }
  .badge-eco { background: rgba(255, 56, 96, 0.15); color: var(--danger); border: 1px solid var(--danger); }

  .search-box { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .search-box input, .search-box select { flex: 1; min-width: 200px; padding: 14px 18px; background: rgba(0, 6, 15, 0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3); border-radius: 8px; color: var(--text); font-family: 'Consolas', monospace; font-size: 14px; }
  .search-box input:focus, .search-box select:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--accent); box-shadow: var(--glow); }
  .btn { padding: 12px 24px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-2), var(--accent)); border: none; border-radius: 8px; color: #000; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: all 0.3s; font-family: inherit; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: var(--glow); }
  .btn-outline { background: transparent; color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid var(--accent); }
  .btn-outline:hover { background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1); }
  .btn-ai { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7, #a29bfe); color: #fff; }
  .btn-ai:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(162, 155, 254, 0.6); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 30px; }
  .timeline::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 10px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 2px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent), transparent); }
  .tl-item { position: relative; padding-bottom: 20px; }
  .tl-item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: -26px; top: 4px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent); }
  .tl-date { font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .tl-title { font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 600; }
  .tl-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 4px; line-height: 1.6; }

  .progress-row { margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .progress-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--text-dim); }
  .progress-bar { height: 8px; background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
  .progress-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-2), var(--accent)); box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent); position: relative; transition: width 1s; }
  .progress-fill::after { content: ''; position: absolute; right: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 20px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.4)); }
  .progress-fill.danger { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b6b, var(--danger)); box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--danger); }
  .progress-fill.warn { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffa502, var(--warn)); box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--warn); }
  .progress-fill.ok { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2ed573, var(--ok)); box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--ok); }

  .bar-chart { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 15px; height: 200px; padding: 20px 0; }
  .bar-item { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  .bar { width: 100%; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2)); border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0; position: relative; min-height: 10px; transition: height 1s; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3); }
  .bar::after { content: attr(data-val); position: absolute; top: -25px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); font-size: 12px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
  .bar-label { margin-top: 8px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); text-align: center; }

  /* 【修复点】移除 transform: scale，仅使用 filter 发光，防止 SVG 原生 translate 冲突导致的抖动 */
  .boiler-diagram { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 750px; background: #0c101d; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
  .boiler-svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; }
  .boiler-zone { cursor: pointer; transition: filter 0.3s ease; }
  .boiler-zone:hover { filter: brightness(1.4) drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.8)); }
  
  .scan-line { position: fixed; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent), transparent); opacity: 0.3; z-index: 99; pointer-events: none; animation: scan 6s linear infinite; }
  @keyframes scan { 0% { top: 0; opacity: 0; } 10% { opacity: 0.3; } 90% { opacity: 0.3; } 100% { top: 100vh; opacity: 0; } }

  .comp-tabs { display: flex; gap: 4px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); flex-wrap: wrap;}
  .comp-tab { padding: 10px 16px; background: transparent; border: none; color: var(--text-dim); cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; letter-spacing: 1px; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transition: all 0.3s; }
  .comp-tab:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .comp-tab.active { color: var(--accent); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }

  .info-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; }
  .info-item { padding: 12px; background: rgba(0, 6, 15, 0.6); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1); border-radius: 6px; }
  .info-item .k { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .info-item .v { font-size: 15px; margin-top: 4px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }

  .alert { padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-left: 4px solid; display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 13px; }
  .alert-info { background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .alert-warn { background: rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.08); border-color: var(--warn); }
  .alert-danger { background: rgba(255, 56, 96, 0.08); border-color: var(--danger); }

  .tube-detail { padding: 20px; background: rgba(0, 17, 34, 0.8); border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 15px; }
  .tube-detail h3 { font-family: 'Consolas', monospace; color: var(--accent); font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5); display: flex; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;}

  .log-box { margin-top: 15px; padding: 15px; background: rgba(0, 6, 15, 0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); border-radius: 6px; font-family: 'Consolas', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: var(--ok); height: 150px; overflow-y: auto; display: none; }
  .code-preview { background: rgba(0, 6, 15, 0.8); border: 1px dashed rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3); padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 15px; font-family: 'Consolas', monospace; font-size: 13px; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1.8; max-height: 200px; overflow-y: auto; }
  .code-preview span { color: var(--text-dim); }
  .fmt-seg { display: inline-block; padding: 4px 8px; margin: 3px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: 'Consolas', monospace; background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); }

  .ai-metric-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .ai-metric { text-align: center; padding: 20px 15px; background: rgba(0,29,61,0.5); border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.2); border-radius: 8px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;}
  .ai-metric::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #a29bfe, transparent); }
  .ai-metric .val { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #a29bfe; font-family: 'Consolas', monospace; text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(162,155,254,0.5); }
  .ai-metric .label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 8px; letter-spacing: 1px;}
  .ai-chart-container { width: 100%; height: 320px; background: rgba(0,6,15,0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.2); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; position: relative;}
  .ai-report { font-family: 'Consolas', 'Microsoft YaHei', monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--accent-3); min-height: 100px; border-left: 3px solid #a29bfe; padding: 20px; background: rgba(162,155,254,0.03); border-radius: 4px; white-space: pre-wrap; }
  .ai-cursor { display: inline-block; width: 8px; height: 16px; background: #a29bfe; animation: blink 1s infinite; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 2px; }
  @keyframes blink { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0; } }
  .loading-spinner { display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; border: 3px solid rgba(162,155,254,0.2); border-radius: 50%; border-top-color: #a29bfe; animation: spin 1s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

  .mini-chart { width: 100%; height: 120px; background: rgba(0,6,15,0.6); border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.1); border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 15px; }

  footer { padding: 25px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15); color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; height: 8px; } ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg-0); } ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--accent-2); border-radius: 4px; } ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: var(--accent); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="bg-grid"></div>
<div class="bg-glow"></div>
<div class="scan-line"></div>

<header>
  <div class="logo">
    <div class="logo-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2L2 7v10l10 5 10-5V7L12 2zm0 2.3l7.5 3.7L12 11.7 4.5 8 12 4.3zM4 9.5l7 3.5v7l-7-3.5v-7zm16 0v7l-7 3.5v-7l7-3.5z"/></svg></div>
    <div class="logo-text">
      <h1>BOILER-TUBE LIFECYCLE SYSTEM</h1>
      <p>锅炉受热面全寿命管理系统 v7.3 (湛江电厂稳定版)</p>
